originalText.text: De is the best personal trainer you could ask for! She is so knowledgeable and her focus on progressive strength training and proper form has taught me so much that I have been able to apply to my workouts and overall lifestyle. As a 1:1 trainer and group fitness leader, De is motivating, efficient, and always makes it fun. Truly the only PT you will need!!

originalText.text: Deanna is a tough but an amazing personal trainer! She listens to my demands and pushes me to exceed them. Every workout is a bit different with underlying consistencies to help improve overall. There has never been a workout in the 6 months where I am not sore, but also fulfilled. I feel like I truly get my money's worth and she has to much more to offer than the typical PT!

originalText.text: I started working out with Deanna during my pregnancy, and had personal workouts with her. As my dedicated workout trainer, De provided invaluable support with safe and effective core workouts and strength training, showcasing her exceptional knowledge in guiding pregnant moms to be, towards maintaining (or even setting) a healthy and active lifestyle while focusing on my specific needs which were preparing for labor, streghtening my core, safe stretches and workouts while guiding me on what is and isn't recommended during pregnancy workouts. She is also supportive in between sessions and overall has vast knowledge that supported me in the process.

originalText.text: Our Team at OPM Pros has had the great opportunity to work with Deanna for a company wellness initiative over several sessions.  She provided a well tailored program for our team, to get everyone moving again, after working remotely for over 15 months.  She provided a variety of exercises techniques, tips and tricks to help with mobility, flexibility and stretching.  This was our first virtual wellness experience, but not our last with Deanna.  Her vibrant personality and coaching skills always kept our team coming back for more.  We look forward to connecting again in the future - Thank you!

originalText.text: 100% satisfied customer. I wanted a personal trainer to help me get back into a fitness regiment. Deanna helped me twice a week for numerous months with functional movement patterns. I learned how to deadlift and squat properly, how to pace myself through cardio vascular workouts, and overall felt great each and every time after we worked out. She inspires you to train and be motivated to keep coming back.
